Effective: October 1, 1999 - March 31, 2000 (for hotel stay)
ANA is pleased to assist busy executives with the features and benefits
of ANA Business Privilege. From the moment you leave to the time you
return, ANA Business Privilege benefits will be with you all the way!
ROUND-TRIP LIMOUSINE SERVIGE
Our private limousine will provide you
with a hassle free trip to and from
your home and the airport.
Limousine service is only available to / from the following airports: New York-JFK,
Los Angeles-LAX, San Francisco-SFO, Washington, D.C.-Dulles, Boston-Logan and
Chicago-O'Hare (Up to 60 miles each way).
SPECIAL HOTEL DISCOUNTS
Save up to 75% at one or any combination
of the 18 selected hotels in Japan.*
You can stay up to four nights and the
hotel stay does not have to be consecutive.
You can also earn 300-500 hotel miles
with your ANA Mileage Club membership
(per night, per room).
